# Pre-action Requirements
1. Review project directory structure before making any changes
2. Understand the current organization of files and their purposes
3. Maintain minimalist folder structure:
   - Keep Docker files in docker/
   - Keep source code in src/
   - Keep configuration files at root level
   - Avoid creating unnecessary subdirectories

# Interaction Rules
1. Execute only explicitly requested actions
2. Ask before making assumptions
3. Provide brief suggestions when relevant
4. Wait for approval before implementing changes
5. Focus on current needs, not future-proofing
6. Use concise communication
